                ullam ea cum sint fuga quis quas numquam in obcaecati autem expedita eius illo nam, odio minus mollitia.
                Sed, cumque?</p>
            <a href="/campgrounds" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary bg-white">View Campgrounds</a>
        </main>


    </div>
    <footer class="footer">&copy;YelpCamp 2022</footer>


    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
